I know of CAP.  I looked at the source that we had (pre 60) and it only
supported the Ethernet port as far as I could tell.  Also, it seems
that it only handles EtherTalk phase 1 and not phase 2.

I may be seriously mistaken, but this is my last checking.  I think
it is high time I take a look at it again.  Perhaps a port to Linux
could be a fun thing to do.

